Wild Atlantic Tae is located beside the most recognisable lighthouse on the Wild Atlantic Way, Fanad Lighthouse at Fanad Head.

Based in a cool custom made coffee wagon, Wild Atlantic Tae offer award winning coffee, freshly roasted, freshly ground and expertly brewed to bring you the amazing coffees, awesome teas and comforting hot chocolate , plus scrumptious homemade baking and homemade Italian Ice Cream.

Visitors to Fanad Head get to enjoy the most breath-taking views of the Lighthouse the Wild Atlantic Ocean also the rugged Donegal Coastline, along with some of the best coffee they will find on the Wild Atlantic Way. So sit back enjoy and take in the unforgettable views from Tory Island all the way round to Dunree Head.
